snippet.title: Codestar
snippet.description: Codestar is a part of Ordina that specializes in Reactive Streambased programming, mostly in Scala. Because knowledge sharing is important to us we will sharing interesting talks we gave on this channel. More about us on our website https://www.codestar.nl/
